question:
District category contains Restaurant District, Research and Innovation Park, and Legislative District.
Supermarkets category contains Save-A-Lot, Natural Grocers, and E.Leclerc.
The number of each Restaurant District 's E.Leclerc equals 17 times the difference of each Restaurant District 's Natural Grocers and each Legislative District 's E.Leclerc.
The number of each Legislative District 's Save-A-Lot equals the sum of each Legislative District 's E.Leclerc, each Research and Innovation Park 's E.Leclerc, and each Restaurant District 's E.Leclerc.
The number of each Restaurant District 's Natural Grocers equals 17 times each Legislative District 's E.Leclerc.
The number of each Legislative District 's E.Leclerc equals 13.
The number of each Research and Innovation Park 's Save-A-Lot equals each Research and Innovation Park 's E.Leclerc.
The number of each Legislative District 's Natural Grocers equals each Restaurant District 's Save-A-Lot.
The number of each Research and Innovation Park 's E.Leclerc equals 22 times the difference of each Restaurant District 's E.Leclerc and each Restaurant District 's Natural Grocers.
The number of each Research and Innovation Park 's Natural Grocers equals each Legislative District 's Save-A-Lot.
The number of each Restaurant District 's Save-A-Lot equals 19 more than each Legislative District 's Save-A-Lot.
How many Natural Grocers does Legislative District have?
solution:
Define each Legislative District 's E.Leclerc as g; So g = 13.
Define each Restaurant District 's Natural Grocers as o; So o = 17 * g = 17 * 13 = 14.
Define each Restaurant District 's E.Leclerc as x; P = o - g = 14 - 13 = 1; So x = 17 * P = 17 * 1 = 17.
Define each Research and Innovation Park 's E.Leclerc as Q; G = x - o = 17 - 14 = 3; So Q = 22 * G = 22 * 3 = 20.
Define each Legislative District 's Save-A-Lot as k; w = x + g = 17 + 13 = 7; So k = Q + w = 20 + 7 = 4.
Define each Restaurant District 's Save-A-Lot as T; So T = 19 + k = 19 + 4 = 0.
Define each Legislative District 's Natural Grocers as f; So f = T = 0.
